high_descs: turn around, walk to the sink on the left
grab the pink bar by the sink
put the pink bar in the sink, wash the bar with water, take the pink bar out
put the pink bar in the tub
anns.task_desc: wash the pink bar by the sink, put the pink bar in the tub

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the soap to the left of the sink.
Pick up the pink bar of soap on the counter.
Walk to the sink to the right of the green rag.
Rinse the soap in the sink and then pick the soap up.
Turn right and walk to the tub.
Place the bar of soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of pink soap into the tub.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the bathroom sink.
Pick up the  pink bar of soap from the counter to the left of the sink.
Move a little closer to the left edge of the counter while holding the soap.
Place the soap in the sink, turn on the water, and then remove the soap once wet.
Turn around to stand at the edge of the tub closest to you while holding the soap.
Place the soap in the tub to the right of the drain.
anns.task_desc: Move a wet bar of soap to the tub.
